                        <interp inst="t18390708-name-96" type="given" value="SAMUEL"></interp>SAMUEL GALL</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No.</hi> 394.) I took charge of the prisoner with the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">Property produced and sworn to.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I picked up the handkerchief, as I was, walking along Long-lane, put it into my pocket, crowed over the road, and the gen<lb></lb>tleman crossed and seized me.</p>
